{"tid":392524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話有言論自由，但係又話言論自由唔係乜都講得。","createTime":"2017-09-08T14:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T10:19:27.000Z","uid":27451,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6534629cb6c4a7ee29fa3954ee75a8a2111154","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"咁即係有無言論自己呀？<br />\n<br />\n我好撚亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332fd3fdc6f8fec32ed8ceeef2bb5d4bb2ea875","tid":392524,"uid":93784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"因為班高官都係無學識囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由呢班共產黨管治香港一定係玩死香港<br />\n佢地唔識界定言論自由, 亦唔會捍衛, 只係識有問題就收緊"},{"pid":"53ebfe9804483d616f43ca9be083a6e0e47244ae","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為班高官都係無學識囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由呢班共產黨管治香港一定係玩死香港<br />\n佢地唔識界定言論自由, 亦唔會捍衛, 只係識有問題就收緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n配合埋奶共傳媒，奶共政黨，五毛狗大合奏。"},{"pid":"b39ce0998c3093809735e6bed8313985dd440458","tid":392524,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"佢就咩都講得，你就⋯⋯要佢批准你講先講得！"},{"pid":"ebf246315d339994f6c048bb2a094f7bc45439a4","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢就咩都講得，你就⋯⋯要佢批准你講先講得！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地咁大班藍絲做戲，要人有人要乜都得。<br />\n<br />\n其實依家香港同大陸已經好接近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a406ddedb75173c9d046cf63a5dc1e611db7575","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"乜野講得乜野唔講得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39cde6402e5def550498a2427fe23c2350064b3","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eb676fce717ffd0c8cfa665b35dbd72dff7c01","tid":392524,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"你有權講野，人地都有權批評你<br />\n不過今次班學生又小氣，又敢做唔敢認，超樣衰！<br />\n<br />\n唔被得人話，佢地有自由幸災樂禍，人地無自由媽交叉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55064f96d3ee21af3f175d15c3a0b7b2eb34f9a6","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有權講野，人地都有權批評你<br />\n不過今次班學生又小氣，又敢做唔敢認，超樣衰！<br />\n<br />\n唔被得人話，佢地有自由幸災樂禍，人地無自由媽交叉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但台戲好假囉，出動咁多人攪兩個學生仔？"},{"pid":"028ac070525d703cabc7d9691590b3b4f0199bb9","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你有權講野，人地都有權批評你<br />\n不過今次班學生又小氣，又敢做唔敢認，超樣衰！<br />\n<br />\n唔被得人話，佢地有自由幸災樂禍，人地無自由媽交叉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但台戲好假囉，出動咁多人攪兩個學生仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到佢地犯左好重罪咁，鳩up都要畀成班奶狗咁批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a84785832036c8f090b0aba6990961883e3e33","tid":392524,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有權講野，人地都有權批評你<br />\n不過今次班學生又小氣，又敢做唔敢認，超樣衰！<br />\n<br />\n唔被得人話，佢地有自由幸災樂禍，人地無自由媽交叉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n媽叉冇問題呀，而家係起底加想踢出校。咁都算自由？"},{"pid":"168d45b11cfaeaae6dbccf72185e0514d7099251","tid":392524,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci